<html lang="en" dir="ltr" x-data="{
          theme: localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'system',
          initTheme() {
              this.applyTheme(this.theme);
              $watch('theme', (newTheme) =&gt; {
                  this.applyTheme(newTheme);
                  localStorage.setItem('theme', newTheme);
              });
          },
          applyTheme(newTheme) {
              if (newTheme === 'dark') {
                  document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
              } else if (newTheme === 'light') {
                  document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
              } else {
                  if (window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches) {
                      document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
                  } else {
                      document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
                  }
              }
          },
          isMobileMenuOpen: false,
          toggleMobileMenu() { this.isMobileMenuOpen = !this.isMobileMenuOpen; }
      }" x-init="initTheme()" data-theme="light"><head>

            <div class="relative" x-data="{ themeMenuOpen: false,theme: localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'system',
                        init() {
                            this.updateTheme();
                            $watch('theme', () =&gt; this.updateTheme());
                        },
                        updateTheme() {
                            localStorage.setItem('theme', this.theme);
                            if (this.theme === 'dark' || (this.theme === 'system' &amp;&amp; window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)) {
                                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'dark');
                            } else {
                                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', 'light');
                            }
                        } }" @click.away="themeMenuOpen = false">
                <button @click="themeMenuOpen = !themeMenuOpen" type="button" class="p-2 rounded-full text-black dark:text-white hover:bg-light-hover-bg dark:hover:bg-gray-700 hover:text-light-text dark:hover:text-gray-200 focus:outline-none">
                    <span class="sr-only">app.change_theme</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-sun" x-show="theme === 'light' || (theme === 'system' &amp;&amp; !window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)"></i>
                    <i class="fas fa-moon" x-show="theme === 'dark' || (theme === 'system' &amp;&amp; window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)" style="display: none;"></i>
                </button>
                <div x-show="themeMenuOpen" x-transition="" class="absolute z-30 right-0 mt-2 w-36 origin-top-right rounded-md shadow-lg bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 ring-1 ring-black ring-opacity-5 focus:outline-none border border-light-border dark:border-gray-600 py-1" style="display: none;">
                    <button @click="theme = 'light'; themeMenuOpen = false;" :class="{ 'bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-600 text-brand-purple dark:text-white': theme === 'light' }" class="w-full text-left flex items-center px-4 py-2 text-sm text-light-text dark:text-gray-200 hover:bg-light-hover-bg dark:hover:bg-gray-600">

                        <i class="fas fa-moon mr-2 w-4"></i> Dark Mode

                '[strong Tunis Southern accent]': { name: 'تونسية جنوبية', icon: 'fa-map-pin', color: 'accent' },
                '[strong Casablanca accent]': { name: 'لهجة الدار البيضاء', icon: 'fa-map-pin', color: 'accent' },
                '[strong Rabat accent]': { name: 'لهجة الرباط', icon: 'fa-map-pin', color: 'accent' },
                '[strong Fes accent]': { name: 'لهجة فاس', icon: 'fa-map-pin', color: 'accent' },
                '[strong Marrakesh accent]': { name: 'لهجة مراكش', icon: 'fa-map-pin', color: 'accent' },
                '[strong Tripoli accent]': { name: 'لهجة طرابلس', icon: 'fa-map-pin', color: 'accent' },
                '[strong Benghazi accent]': { name: 'لهجة بنغازي', icon: 'fa-map-pin', color: 'accent' }
            }
        };

        // Flatten all tags for easier processing
        const ALL_EMOTION_TAGS = {};
        Object.values(EMOTION_TAGS).forEach(category => {
            Object.assign(ALL_EMOTION_TAGS, category);
        });

        // Translation strings
        const translations = {
            none: "None",
            error: "Error",
            errorNetwork: "A network error occurred. Please check your internet connection and try again.",
            generateFailed: "Audio generation failed. Please check your text and try again.",
            selectVoiceError: "Please select a voice first before generating speech.",
            yourTextValidation: "You have submitted empty fields. Please double-check the fields and try again.",

            playOrPause: "Play/Pause",

            featureLockedMessage: "This feature is available only for subscribers. Please upgrade to enjoy full access.",
            customPromptLockedMessage: "Custom Prompt mode is only available for subscribers. Please upgrade for full control over voice performance.",
            previewLockedMessage: "Preview feature is only available for subscribers. Upgrade to preview texts without credit deduction.",
            addToFavorites: "Add to Favorites",
            removeFromFavorites: "Remove from Favorites",

            noPerformanceSelectedDisplay: "No performance selected",
            defaultDialectImg: "https://lahajati.ai/storage/flag/choice.png",
            defaultPerformanceImg: "https://lahajati.ai/storage/avatars/choice.png",

    multiGenerationLocked: "Multi-generation feature is available for subscribers only",
    multiGenerationProgress: "Multi-Generation Progress",

        // DOM Ready
        document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
            console.log('Initializing TTS Superior with Multi-Generation...');
            
            // Initialize all components
            initTabSwitching();
            initVoiceTabSwitching();
            initFileUpload();
            initEmotionSystem();
            initVoiceSelection();
            initAudioGeneration();
            initSpeedControl();
            initFilters();
            initSearch();
            initAudioPlayer();
            initTextEditors();
            initProjectName();
            initAdvancedOptions();
            initProFeatures();
            initDialectAndPerformance();
            initPreviewFeature();
            initMultiGeneration(); // New function
            
            // Load stored preferences
            loadStoredPreferences();
            
            // Initialize character count for all editors
            updateAllCharCounts();
            
            // Apply initial filters
            applyFilters();
            
            console.log('TTS Superior initialization complete with Multi-Generation.');
        });

        // ============ MULTI-GENERATION FUNCTIONS ============
        function initMultiGeneration() {
            console.log('Initializing Multi-Generation feature...');
            
            // Initialize count buttons
            const countButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.count-btn');
            countButtons.forEach(btn => {
                btn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    if (btn.disabled) {
                        if (USER_PACKAGE_VALUE <= 1) {
                            showError('ميزة التوليد المتعدد متاحة للمشتركين فقط');
                        }
                        return;
                    }
                    
                    // Update active state
                    countButtons.forEach(b => b.classList.remove('active'));
                    btn.classList.add('active');
                    
                    // Update selected count
                    selectedGenerationCount = parseInt(btn.dataset.count);
                    console.log('Selected generation count:', selectedGenerationCount);
                    
                    // Store preference
                    localStorage.setItem('selected_generation_count', selectedGenerationCount);
                });
            });
            
            // Initialize modal
            initMultiGenerationModal();
            
            // Load stored count
            const storedCount = localStorage.getItem('selected_generation_count');
            if (storedCount && parseInt(storedCount) <= MAX_GENERATIONS) {
                const btn = document.querySelector(`[data-count="${storedCount}"]`);
                if (btn && !btn.disabled) {
                    btn.click();
                }
            }
            
            console.log('Multi-Generation feature initialized successfully');
        }
        
        function initMultiGenerationModal() {
            multiGenerationModal = document.getElementById('multi-generation-modal');
            const closeBtn = document.getElementById('close-multi-modal');
            
            if (closeBtn) {
                closeBtn.addEventListener('click', closeMultiGenerationModal);
            }
            
            // Close on backdrop click
            if (multiGenerationModal) {
                multiGenerationModal.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                    if (e.target === multiGenerationModal) {
                        closeMultiGenerationModal();
                    }
                });
            }
        }
        
        function showMultiGenerationModal() {
            if (!multiGenerationModal) return;
            
            console.log('Showing multi-generation modal for', selectedGenerationCount, 'generations');
            
            // Clear previous generations
            currentGenerations = [];
            Object.keys(generationWaveSurfers).forEach(key => {
                if (generationWaveSurfers[key]) {
                    generationWaveSurfers[key].destroy();
                }
            });
            generationWaveSurfers = {};
            
            // Create generation items
            const container = document.getElementById('generation-items');
            if (!container) return;
            
            container.innerHTML = '';
            
            for (let i = 1; i <= selectedGenerationCount; i++) {
                const generationId = `gen_${Date.now()}_${i}`;
                const item = createGenerationItem(generationId, i);
                container.appendChild(item);
                
                currentGenerations.push({
                    id: generationId,
                    index: i,
                    status: 'waiting',
                    progress: 0,
                    audioUrl: null,
                    error: null
                });
            }
            
            multiGenerationModal.style.display = 'flex';
            
            // Start generations
            setTimeout(() => {
                startMultipleGenerations();
            }, 500);
        }
        
function createGenerationItem(generationId, index) {
    const item = document.createElement('div');
    item.className = 'generation-item loading';
    item.id = generationId;
    
    // استخدام الترجمات من المتغير
    const copyTitle = "Copy :number".replace(':number', index);
    const loadingText = "Generating...";
    const playText = "Play";
    const downloadText = "Download";
    
    item.innerHTML = `
        <div class="generation-item-header">
            <div class="generation-item-title">${copyTitle}</div>
            <div class="generation-item-status loading">
                <div class="generation-spinner"></div>
                <span>${loadingText}</span>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="generation-item-progress">
            <div class="generation-item-progress-bar" style="width: 0%"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="generation-item-actions">
            <button class="generation-action-btn primary" onclick="playGenerationAudio('${generationId}')">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-play"></i>
                ${playText}
            </button>
            <button class="generation-action-btn" onclick="downloadGenerationAudio('${generationId}')">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-download"></i>
                ${downloadText}
            </button>
        </div>
    `;
    
    return item;
}

        
        function startMultipleGenerations() {
            console.log('Starting multiple generations...');
            
            const text = getCurrentText();
            
            if (!text.trim()) {
                showError('يرجى إدخال نص للتحويل');
                closeMultiGenerationModal();
                return;
            }
            
            if (!selectedVoiceId) {
                showError('يرجى اختيار صوت أولاً');
                closeMultiGenerationModal();
                return;
            }
            
            // Check balance for multiple generations
            const textLength = countEffectiveCharacters(text);
            const totalCost = textLength * selectedGenerationCount;
            
            if (USER_PACKAGE_VALUE <= 4) {
                const currentBalance = parseInt(document.getElementById("BalanceUser").textContent.replace(/\D/g,'')) || 0;
                if (currentBalance < totalCost) {
                    showError(`لا تملك نقاط كافية. تحتاج ${totalCost} نقطة ولديك ${currentBalance} نقطة`);
                    closeMultiGenerationModal();
                    return;
                }
            }
            
            // Start all generations simultaneously
            currentGenerations.forEach(generation => {
                updateGenerationStatus(generation.id, 'loading', 'Generating...');
                generateSingleAudio(generation.id, text, false);
            });
        }
        
        function generateSingleAudio(generationId, text, isPreview = false) {
            console.log('Generating audio for:', generationId);
            
            const formData = new FormData();
            formData.append('text', text.replace(/[\r\n]+/g, ' ').trim());
            formData.append('id_voice', selectedVoiceId);
            formData.append('version', 'lahajati_tts_pro_v1');
            formData.append('feature_mode', 5);
            formData.append('input_mode', currentInputMode);
            formData.append('speed', currentSpeed);
            formData.append('temperature', currentTemperature);
            formData.append('top_p', currentTopP);
            formData.append('top_k', currentTopK);
            formData.append('is_preview', isPreview ? 1 : 0);
            formData.append('generation_id', generationId);

            const proQualityToggle = document.getElementById('pro-quality-toggle');
            const proQualityToggle1 = document.getElementById('pro-quality-toggle1');
            
            if (proQualityToggle) {
                formData.append('professional_quality', proQualityToggle.checked ? 1 : 0);
            }
            
            if (proQualityToggle1) {
                formData.append('improve_human', proQualityToggle1.checked ? 1 : 0);
            }

            const projectName = document.getElementById('project-name-input')?.value;
            if (projectName) {
                formData.append('project_name', projectName + ` - نسخة ${getGenerationIndex(generationId)}`);
            }

            if (currentInputMode === 'custom_prompt') {
                const customPrompt = document.getElementById('custom-prompt-text')?.value;
                if (customPrompt) {
                    formData.append('custom_prompt_text', customPrompt);
                }
            }

            if (selectedDialectId) {
                formData.append('dialect_id', selectedDialectId);
            }
            if (selectedPerformanceId) {
                formData.append('performance_id', selectedPerformanceId);
            }

            // Simulate progress
            let progress = 0;
            const progressInterval = setInterval(() => {
                progress += Math.random() * 15;
                if (progress > 90) progress = 90;
                updateGenerationProgress(generationId, progress);
            }, 500);

            fetch("https://lahajati.ai/en/tools/text-to-speech", {
                method: "POST",
                body: formData,
                headers: {
                    'Accept': 'text/plain',
                    'X-CSRF-TOKEN': csrfToken
                }
            })
            .then(response => {
                clearInterval(progressInterval);
                
                if (!response.ok) {
                    return response.text().then(raw => {
                        let msg = raw || response.statusText;
                        try {
                            const parsed = JSON.parse(raw);
                            if (parsed && typeof parsed.message === 'string') {
                                msg = parsed.message;
                            }
                        } catch (_) {}
                        throw {
                            status: response.status,
                            data: { message: msg }
                        };
                    });
                }
                return response.text();
            })
            .then(data => {
                console.log('Audio generated successfully for:', generationId);
                
                updateGenerationProgress(generationId, 100);
                
                const audioUrl = 'data:audio/wav;base64,' + data;
                
                // Update generation data
                const generation = currentGenerations.find(g => g.id === generationId);
                if (generation) {
                    generation.status = 'completed';
                    generation.audioUrl = audioUrl;
                }
                
                // Update UI
                updateGenerationStatus(generationId, 'completed', 'مكتمل');
                updateGenerationProgress(generationId, 100);
                
                // Initialize waveform for this generation
                initGenerationWaveform(generationId, audioUrl);
                
                // Update balance only once when first generation completes
                if (USER_PACKAGE_VALUE <= 4) {
                    const completedCount = currentGenerations.filter(g => g.status === 'completed').length;
                    if (completedCount === 1) {
                        const currentBalance = parseInt(document.getElementById("BalanceUser").textContent.replace(/\D/g,'')) || 0;
                        const cost = countEffectiveCharacters(getCurrentText()) * selectedGenerationCount;
                        const newBalance = Math.max(0, currentBalance - cost);
                        document.getElementById("BalanceUser").textContent = newBalance;
                        if (document.getElementById("userBalanceNavBar")) {
                            document.getElementById("userBalanceNavBar").textContent = newBalance;
                        }
                    }
                }
            })
            .catch(error => {
                clearInterval(progressInterval);
                console.error('Generation error for', generationId, ':', error);
                
                const generation = currentGenerations.find(g => g.id === generationId);
                if (generation) {
                    generation.status = 'error';
                    generation.error = error?.data?.message || 'خطأ في التوليد';
                }
                
                updateGenerationStatus(generationId, 'error', generation.error);
                updateGenerationProgress(generationId, 0);
            });
        }
        
        function updateGenerationStatus(generationId, status, message) {
            const item = document.getElementById(generationId);
            if (!item) return;
            
            item.className = `generation-item ${status}`;
            
            const statusEl = item.querySelector('.generation-item-status');
            if (!statusEl) return;
            
            statusEl.className = `generation-item-status ${status}`;
            
            let icon = '';
            switch (status) {
                case 'loading':
                    icon = '<div class="generation-spinner"></div>';
                    break;
                case 'completed':
                    icon = '<i class="fa-solid fa-check generation-completed-icon"></i>';
                    break;
                case 'error':
                    icon = '<i class="fa-solid fa-exclamation-triangle generation-error-icon"></i>';
                    break;
            }
            
            statusEl.innerHTML = `${icon}<span>${message}</span>`;
        }
        
        function updateGenerationProgress(generationId, progress) {
            const item = document.getElementById(generationId);
            if (!item) return;
            
            const progressBar = item.querySelector('.generation-item-progress-bar');
            if (progressBar) {
                progressBar.style.width = `${progress}%`;
                if (progress >= 100) {
                    progressBar.classList.add('completed');
                }
            }
        }
        
        function getGenerationIndex(generationId) {
            const generation = currentGenerations.find(g => g.id === generationId);
            return generation ? generation.index : 1;
        }
        
        function initGenerationWaveform(generationId, audioUrl) {
            const item = document.getElementById(generationId);
            if (!item) return;
            
            // Create waveform container if not exists
            let waveformContainer = item.querySelector('.generation-waveform');
            if (!waveformContainer) {
                waveformContainer = document.createElement('div');
                waveformContainer.className = 'generation-waveform';
                waveformContainer.style.cssText = 'height: 40px; margin: 8px 0; border-radius: 4px; overflow: hidden;';
                
                const progressContainer = item.querySelector('.generation-item-progress');
                if (progressContainer) {
                    progressContainer.parentNode.insertBefore(waveformContainer, progressContainer.nextSibling);
                }
            }
            
            if (typeof WaveSurfer !== 'undefined') {
                try {
                    const wavesurfer = WaveSurfer.create({
                        container: waveformContainer,
                        waveColor: "#e5e7eb",
                        progressColor: "#10b981",
                        cursorColor: "#059669",
                        height: 40,
                        barWidth: 1,
                        barGap: 1,
                        responsive: true,
                        backend: 'MediaElement'
                    });
                    
                    wavesurfer.load(audioUrl);
                    generationWaveSurfers[generationId] = wavesurfer;
                    
                    wavesurfer.on('ready', () => {
                        console.log('Waveform ready for:', generationId);
                    });
                    
                } catch (error) {
                    console.error('Error creating waveform for', generationId, ':', error);
                }
            }
        }
        
        function playGenerationAudio(generationId) {
            const generation = currentGenerations.find(g => g.id === generationId);
            if (!generation || !generation.audioUrl) return;
            
            // Stop main player if playing
            if (globalMainPlayerWaveSurfer?.isPlaying()) {
                globalMainPlayerWaveSurfer.pause();
            }
            
            // Stop other generation players
            Object.keys(generationWaveSurfers).forEach(key => {
                if (key !== generationId && generationWaveSurfers[key]?.isPlaying()) {
                    generationWaveSurfers[key].pause();
                }
            });
            
            // Play this generation
            if (generationWaveSurfers[generationId]) {
                generationWaveSurfers[generationId].playPause();
            } else {
                // Fallback to main player
                playGeneratedAudio(generation.audioUrl.replace('data:audio/wav;base64,', ''));
                closeMultiGenerationModal();
            }
        }
        
        function downloadGenerationAudio(generationId) {
            const generation = currentGenerations.find(g => g.id === generationId);
            if (!generation || !generation.audioUrl) return;
            
            const link = document.createElement('a');
            link.href = generation.audioUrl;
            link.download = `lahajati_${selectedVoiceName}_نسخة${generation.index}_${Date.now()}.mp3`;
            document.body.appendChild(link);
            link.click();
            document.body.removeChild(link);
        }
        
        function closeMultiGenerationModal() {
            if (!multiGenerationModal) return;
            
            multiGenerationModal.style.display = 'none';
            
            // Clean up waveforms
            Object.keys(generationWaveSurfers).forEach(key => {
                if (generationWaveSurfers[key]) {
                    try {
                        generationWaveSurfers[key].destroy();
                    } catch (e) {
                        console.log('Waveform cleanup completed for:', key);
                    }
                }
            });
            generationWaveSurfers = {};
            currentGenerations = [];
        }

        // Update the main generation function to handle multi-generation
        function handleGeneration(isPreview = false) {
            const text = getCurrentText();

            console.log('Handling generation with:', {
                text: text.substring(0, 50) + '...',
                mode: currentInputMode,
                voiceId: selectedVoiceId,
                voiceName: selectedVoiceName,
                isPreview: isPreview,
                multipleCount: selectedGenerationCount
            });

            if (!text.trim()) {
                showError('يرجى إدخال نص للتحويل');
                return;
            }

            if (text.length > MAX_CHARS_DEFAULT) {
                showError(`النص طويل جداً. الحد الأقصى ${MAX_CHARS_DEFAULT} حرف`);
                return;
            }

            if (!selectedVoiceId) {
                showError('يرجى اختيار صوت أولاً');
                return;
            }

            if (currentInputMode === 'custom_prompt' && USER_PACKAGE_VALUE < MIN_PACKAGE_FOR_PREMIUM) {
                showError('وضع التوجيه المخصص متاح فقط للمشتركين');
                return;
            }

            if (isPreview && USER_PACKAGE_VALUE < MIN_PACKAGE_FOR_PREMIUM) {
                showError(translations.previewLockedMessage);
                return;
            }

            // Check if multi-generation is requested
            if (selectedGenerationCount > 1 && !isPreview) {
                if (USER_PACKAGE_VALUE <= 1) {
                    showError('ميزة التوليد المتعدد متاحة للمشتركين فقط');
                    return;
                }
                showMultiGenerationModal();
            } else {
                // Single generation
                generateAudio(text, isPreview);
            }
        }

        // Rest of the functions remain the same...
        // [Include all the remaining functions from the original code starting from createAutocompleteDropdown...]

function createAutocompleteDropdown() {
    const dropdown = document.createElement('div');
    dropdown.id = 'emotion-autocomplete-dropdown';
    dropdown.style.cssText = `
        position: absolute;
        background: white;
        border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        max-height: 200px;
        overflow-y: auto;
        z-index: 1001;
        display: none;
        min-width: 200px;
    `;
    
    // للوضع المظلم
    if (document.body.classList.contains('dark')) {
        dropdown.style.background = '#1e293b';
        dropdown.style.borderColor = '#334155';
        dropdown.style.color = '#f1f5f9';
    }
    
    document.body.appendChild(dropdown);
    return dropdown;
}

function createAutocompleteItem(emotionTag, searchTerm) {
    const emotionInfo = ALL_EMOTION_TAGS[emotionTag];
    if (!emotionInfo) return null;
    
    const item = document.createElement('div');
    item.className = 'autocomplete-item';
    item.dataset.emotionTag = emotionTag; // إضافة مهمة!
    item.style.cssText = `
        padding: 8px 12px;
        cursor: pointer;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        transition: background-color 0.2s;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f3f4f6;
        font-size: 14px;
    `;
    
    if (document.body.classList.contains('dark')) {
        item.style.borderColor = '#374151';
        item.style.color = '#f1f5f9';
    }
    
    // تمييز النص المطابق
    let displayName = emotionInfo.name;
    if (searchTerm && searchTerm !== '') {
        const regex = new RegExp(`(${searchTerm})`, 'gi');
        displayName = displayName.replace(regex, '<strong style="color: #10b981;">$1</strong>');
    }
    
    item.innerHTML = `
        <i class="fa-solid ${emotionInfo.icon}" style="color: #6b7280; width: 16px; flex-shrink: 0;"></i>
        <span style="font-weight: 500; flex: 1;">${displayName}</span>
        <span style="font-size: 11px; color: #9ca3af; font-family: monospace;">${emotionTag}</span>
    `;
    
    item.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
        // إزالة التحديد من العناصر الأخرى
        item.parentNode.querySelectorAll('.autocomplete-item').forEach(i => {
            i.classList.remove('selected');
            i.style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';
        });
        
        // تحديد هذا العنصر
        item.classList.add('selected');
        item.style.backgroundColor = document.body.classList.contains('dark') ? '#475569' : '#e5e7eb';
    });
    
    item.addEventListener('mouseleave', () => {
        // لا نزيل التحديد هنا لأن mouse قد يخرج مؤقتاً
    });
    
    item.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        e.stopPropagation();
        selectAutocompleteEmotion(emotionTag);
    });
    
    return item;
}

        // ============ DIALECT AND PERFORMANCE SELECTION ============
        function initDialectAndPerformance() {
            const dialectSelector = document.getElementById('dialect-selector');
            const performanceSelector = document.getElementById('performance-selector');

            if (dialectSelector) {
                dialectSelector.addEventListener('click', openDialectModal);
            }

            if (performanceSelector) {
                performanceSelector.addEventListener('click', openPerformanceModal);
            }

            // Load stored selections
            const storedDialectId = localStorage.getItem('selected_dialect_id');
            if (storedDialectId && allDialects.find(d => d.id == storedDialectId)) {
                const dialect = allDialects.find(d => d.id == storedDialectId);
                selectDialect(dialect);
            }

            const storedPerformanceId = localStorage.getItem('selected_performance_id');
            if (storedPerformanceId && allPerformances.find(p => p.id == storedPerformanceId)) {
                const performance = allPerformances.find(p => p.id == storedPerformanceId);
                selectPerformance(performance);
            }
        }

function openDialectModal() {
    const modal = document.getElementById('dialect-modal');
    const grid = document.getElementById('dialect-options-grid');
    
    // Clear existing content
    grid.innerHTML = '';
    
    // إضافة شريط البحث إذا لم يكن موجوداً
    let searchContainer = modal.querySelector('.modal-search-container');
    if (!searchContainer) {
        searchContainer = document.createElement('div');
        searchContainer.className = 'modal-search-container';
        searchContainer.innerHTML = `
            <i class="fa-solid fa-search modal-search-icon"></i>
            <input type="text" id="dialect-search" class="modal-search-input" placeholder="ابحث عن اللهجة...">
        `;
        modal.querySelector('.modal-body').insertBefore(searchContainer, grid);
        
        // إضافة وظيفة البحث
        const searchInput = searchContainer.querySelector('#dialect-search');
        searchInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
            filterDialectOptions(e.target.value);
        });
    } else {
        // مسح النص السابق
        searchContainer.querySelector('#dialect-search').value = '';
    }
    
    // Add "No Selection" option
    const noSelectionCard = createDialectCard({
        id: '',
        name: translations.noDialectSelectedDisplay,
        description: 'عدم اختيار أي لهجة محددة',
        image: null
    });
    grid.appendChild(noSelectionCard);
    
    // Add all dialects
    allDialects.forEach(dialect => {
        const card = createDialectCard(dialect);
        grid.appendChild(card);
    });
    
    modal.style.display = 'flex';
    
    // التركيز على شريط البحث
    setTimeout(() => {
        searchContainer.querySelector('#dialect-search').focus();
    }, 100);
}


function openPerformanceModal() {
    const modal = document.getElementById('performance-modal');
    const grid = document.getElementById('performance-options-grid');
    
    // Clear existing content
    grid.innerHTML = '';
    
    // إضافة شريط البحث إذا لم يكن موجوداً
    let searchContainer = modal.querySelector('.modal-search-container');
    if (!searchContainer) {
        searchContainer = document.createElement('div');
        searchContainer.className = 'modal-search-container';
        searchContainer.innerHTML = `
            <i class="fa-solid fa-search modal-search-icon"></i>
            <input type="text" id="performance-search" class="modal-search-input" placeholder="ابحث عن أسلوب الأداء...">
        `;
        modal.querySelector('.modal-body').insertBefore(searchContainer, grid);
        
        // إضافة وظيفة البحث
        const searchInput = searchContainer.querySelector('#performance-search');
        searchInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
            filterPerformanceOptions(e.target.value);
        });
    } else {
        // مسح النص السابق
        searchContainer.querySelector('#performance-search').value = '';
    }
    
    // Add "No Selection" option
    const noSelectionCard = createPerformanceCard({
        id: '',
        name: translations.noPerformanceSelectedDisplay,
        description: 'عدم اختيار أي أداء محدد',
        image: null
    });
    grid.appendChild(noSelectionCard);
    
    // Add all performances
    allPerformances.forEach(performance => {
        const card = createPerformanceCard(performance);
        grid.appendChild(card);
    });
    
    modal.style.display = 'flex';
    
    // التركيز على شريط البحث
    setTimeout(() => {
        searchContainer.querySelector('#performance-search').focus();
    }, 100);
}
function filterDialectOptions(searchTerm) {
    const grid = document.getElementById('dialect-options-grid');
    const cards = grid.querySelectorAll('.selection-item');
    
    const searchLower = searchTerm.toLowerCase().trim();
    
    cards.forEach(card => {
        const name = card.querySelector('.selection-name')?.textContent?.toLowerCase() || '';
        const description = card.querySelector('[style*="color: #6b7280"]')?.textContent?.toLowerCase() || '';
        
        const shouldShow = searchLower === '' || 
                          name.includes(searchLower) || 
                          description.includes(searchLower);
        
        card.style.display = shouldShow ? 'block' : 'none';
    });
}

function filterPerformanceOptions(searchTerm) {
    const grid = document.getElementById('performance-options-grid');
    const cards = grid.querySelectorAll('.selection-item');
    
    const searchLower = searchTerm.toLowerCase().trim();
    
    cards.forEach(card => {
        const name = card.querySelector('.selection-name')?.textContent?.toLowerCase() || '';
        const description = card.querySelector('[style*="color: #6b7280"]')?.textContent?.toLowerCase() || '';
        
        const shouldShow = searchLower === '' || 
                          name.includes(searchLower) || 
                          description.includes(searchLower);
        
        card.style.display = shouldShow ? 'block' : 'none';
    });
}

        function createDialectCard(dialect) {
            const card = document.createElement('div');
            card.className = 'selection-item';
            card.style.cssText = 'margin: 0; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;';
            
            const isLocked = dialect.package > USER_PACKAGE_VALUE;
            if (isLocked) {
                card.style.opacity = '0.6';
                card.style.cursor = 'not-allowed';
            }
            
            const imgSrc = dialect.image ? `/storage/${dialect.image}` : translations.defaultDialectImg;
            
            card.innerHTML = `
                <div class="selection-avatar">
                    <img src="${imgSrc}" alt="${dialect.name}">
                </div>
                <div class="selection-info">
                    <div class="selection-name">${dialect.name}</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280;">${dialect.description || ''}</div>
                </div>
            `;
            
            card.addEventListener('click', () => {
                if (!isLocked) {
                    selectDialect(dialect);
                    closeDialectModal();
                } else {
                    showError('هذه اللهجة متاحة للمشتركين فقط');
                }
            });
            
            return card;
        }

        function createPerformanceCard(performance) {
            const card = document.createElement('div');
            card.className = 'selection-item';
            card.style.cssText = 'margin: 0; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s;';
            
            const isLocked = performance.package > USER_PACKAGE_VALUE;
            if (isLocked) {
                card.style.opacity = '0.6';
                card.style.cursor = 'not-allowed';
            }
            
            const imgSrc = performance.image ? `/storage/${performance.image}` : translations.defaultPerformanceImg;
            
            card.innerHTML = `
                <div class="selection-avatar">
                    <img src="${imgSrc}" alt="${performance.name}">
                </div>
                <div class="selection-info">
                    <div class="selection-name">${performance.name}</div>
                    <div style="font-size: 11px; color: #6b7280;">${performance.description || ''}</div>
                </div>
            `;
            
            card.addEventListener('click', () => {
                if (!isLocked) {
                    selectPerformance(performance);
                    closePerformanceModal();
                } else {
                    showError('هذا الأداء متاح للمشتركين فقط');
                }
            });
            
            return card;
        }

        function selectDialect(dialect) {
            selectedDialectId = dialect.id || '';
            selectedDialectName = dialect.name;
            selectedDialectImg = dialect.image ? `/storage/${dialect.image}` : translations.defaultDialectImg;
            
            // Update UI
            document.getElementById('selected-dialect-name').textContent = selectedDialectName;
            document.getElementById('selected-dialect-img').src = selectedDialectImg;
            
            // Store in localStorage
            if (selectedDialectId) {
                localStorage.setItem('selected_dialect_id', selectedDialectId);
            } else {
                localStorage.removeItem('selected_dialect_id');
            }
            
            console.log('Dialect selected:', selectedDialectName);
        }

        function selectPerformance(performance) {
            selectedPerformanceId = performance.id || '';
            selectedPerformanceName = performance.name;
            selectedPerformanceImg = performance.image ? `/storage/${performance.image}` : translations.defaultPerformanceImg;
            
            // Update UI
            document.getElementById('selected-performance-name').textContent = selectedPerformanceName;
            document.getElementById('selected-performance-img').src = selectedPerformanceImg;
            
            // Store in localStorage
            if (selectedPerformanceId) {
                localStorage.setItem('selected_performance_id', selectedPerformanceId);
            } else {
                localStorage.removeItem('selected_performance_id');
            }
            
            console.log('Performance selected:', selectedPerformanceName);
        }

function closeDialectModal() {
    const modal = document.getElementById('dialect-modal');
    modal.style.display = 'none';
    
    // مسح البحث
    const searchInput = modal.querySelector('#dialect-search');
    if (searchInput) {
        searchInput.value = '';
    }
}

function closePerformanceModal() {
    const modal = document.getElementById('performance-modal');
    modal.style.display = 'none';
    
    // مسح البحث
    const searchInput = modal.querySelector('#performance-search');
    if (searchInput) {
        searchInput.value = '';
    }
}


        // ============ PREVIEW FEATURE ============
        function initPreviewFeature() {
            const previewBtn = document.getElementById('preview-btn');
            
            if (previewBtn) {
                previewBtn.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    if (USER_PACKAGE_VALUE < MIN_PACKAGE_FOR_PREMIUM) {
                        showError(translations.previewLockedMessage);
                        return;
                    }
                    handleGeneration(true); // true = is preview
                });
            }
        }

        // ============ TAB SWITCHING ============
        function initTabSwitching() {
            const tabButtons = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-button');
            const tabContents = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content');

            tabButtons.forEach(button => {
                button.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    const targetTab = button.dataset.tab;
                    
                    // Update active states
                    tabButtons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
                    button.classList.add('active');
                    
                    // Show/hide content
                    tabContents.forEach(content => {
                        content.style.display = 'none';
                    });
                    
                    const targetContent = document.getElementById(targetTab + '-content');
                    if (targetContent) {
                        targetContent.style.display = 'block';
                    }
                    
                    // Update current mode
                    currentInputMode = targetTab.replace('-', '_');
                    
                    // Re-initialize editors if needed
if (targetTab === 'emotion-text') {
    // لا تعيد تعيين emotionSystemInitialized هنا
    setTimeout(() => {
        initSmartTextEditor();
    }, 100);
}

setTimeout(() => {
    updateCurrentEditorDirection();
}, 200);

                    // Update character count
                    updateCharCount();
                    
                    console.log('Switched to tab:', targetTab, 'Mode:', currentInputMode);
                });
            });
        }

        // [Include all remaining functions from the original code...]
        // I'll continue with the rest of the functions to maintain the complete functionality

function resetEmotionSystem() {
    emotionSystemInitialized = false;
    isActiveEmotion = false;
    
    // إزالة dropdown إذا كان مفتوحاً
    const dropdown = document.getElementById('emotion-selector-dropdown');
    if (dropdown) {
        dropdown.style.display = 'none';
    }
    
    const trigger = document.getElementById('emotion-selector-trigger');
    if (trigger) {
        trigger.classList.remove('active');
    }
    
    console.log('Emotion system reset');
}

        function initVoiceTabSwitching() {
            const voiceTabs = document.querySelectorAll('.voice-tab');

            voiceTabs.forEach(tab => {
                tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    const targetTab = tab.dataset.voiceTab;
                    
                    // Update active states
                    voiceTabs.forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
                    tab.classList.add('active');
                    
                    // Update current voice tab
                    currentVoiceTab = targetTab;
                    
                    // Update favorites tab if needed
                    if (targetTab === 'favorites') {
                        populateFavoritesTab();
                    }
                    
                    // Filter voices based on selected tab
                    filterVoicesByTab();
                    
                    console.log('Switched to voice tab:', targetTab);
                });
            });
        }

        function populateFavoritesTab() {
            const favoritesContainer = document.getElementById('favorites');
            if (!favoritesContainer) return;

            // Clear existing content
            favoritesContainer.innerHTML = '';
            
            // Find all favorited voices from OpenAI and My Voices tabs
            const openaiVoices = document.querySelectorAll('#openai-voices .voice-card[data-is-favorite="1"]');
            const myVoices = document.querySelectorAll('#my-voices .voice-card[data-is-favorite="1"]');
            
            const allFavorites = [...openaiVoices, ...myVoices];

            if (allFavorites.length === 0) {
                favoritesContainer.innerHTML = `
                    <div style="grid-column: span 2; text-align: center; padding: 40px; color: #6b7280;">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-heart" style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px; opacity: 0.5;"></i>
                        <p style="margin-bottom: 8px; font-weight: 500;">No favorite voices yet</p>
                        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">Add voices to favorites by clicking the heart icon</p>
                    </div>
                `;
            } else {
                allFavorites.forEach(originalCard => {
                    const clonedCard = originalCard.cloneNode(true);
                    // Re-attach event listeners to cloned card
                    attachVoiceCardEvents(clonedCard);
                    favoritesContainer.appendChild(clonedCard);
                });
            }
        }

        function filterVoicesByTab() {
            const voiceTabContents = document.querySelectorAll('.voice-tab-content');
            
            // Hide all voice tab contents first
            voiceTabContents.forEach(content => {
                content.style.display = 'none';
            });
            
            // Show the active tab content
            let activeContent;
            switch (currentVoiceTab) {
                case 'openai':
                    resetEmotionSystem();
                    activeContent = document.getElementById('openai-voices');
                    break;
                case 'my-voices':
                    resetEmotionSystem();
                    activeContent = document.getElementById('my-voices');
                    break;
                case 'favorites':
                    resetEmotionSystem();
                    activeContent = document.getElementById('favorites');
                    break;
            }
            
            if (activeContent) {
                activeContent.style.display = 'grid';
            }
            
            // Apply current filters to visible cards
            applyFilters();
        }

        function attachVoiceCardEvents(card) {
            if (card.dataset.eventsAttached) return;
            card.dataset.eventsAttached = 'true';

            const sampleBtn = card.querySelector('.play-sample-btn');
            const favoriteBtn = card.querySelector('.favorite-btn');

            // Main card click for selection
            card.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                if (e.target.closest('.play-sample-btn') || e.target.closest('.favorite-btn')) {
                    return;
                }

                if (card.classList.contains('locked')) {
                    showError('هذا الصوت متاح فقط للمشتركين');
                    return;
                }

                selectVoice(card);
            });

            // Sample play button
            if (sampleBtn) {
                sampleBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    const sampleUrl = sampleBtn.dataset.sampleUrl;
                    if (sampleUrl) {
                        playVoiceSample(sampleUrl, sampleBtn);
                    } else {
                        showError('لا توجد عينة متاحة لهذا الصوت');
                    }
                });
            }

            // Favorite button
            if (favoriteBtn) {
                favoriteBtn.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                    e.stopPropagation();
                    toggleFavorite(favoriteBtn);
                });
            }
        }

        // ============ CHARACTER LIMITS ============
        function enforceCharacterLimit(input, maxLength) {
            input.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
                const text = e.target.value;
                if (text.length > maxLength) {
                    e.target.value = text.substring(0, maxLength);
                    showTemporaryMessage(`تم الوصول للحد الأقصى: ${maxLength} حرف`, 2000);
                }
                updateCharCount();
            });

            input.addEventListener('paste', (e) => {
                setTimeout(() => {
                    const text = e.target.value;
                    if (text.length > maxLength) {
                        e.target.value = text.substring(0, maxLength);
                        showTemporaryMessage(`تم اقتطاع النص للحد الأقصى: ${maxLength} حرف`, 2000);
                    }
                    updateCharCount();
                }, 10);
            });
        }

        function enforceSmartEditorLimit() {
            const smartEditor = document.getElementById('smart-text-editor');
            if (!smartEditor) return;

            smartEditor.addEventListener('input', () => {
                const plainText = getPlainTextFromEditor();
                const effectiveLength = countEffectiveCharacters(plainText);
                
                if (effectiveLength > MAX_CHARS_DEFAULT) {
                    // Prevent further input
                    const selection = window.getSelection();
                    if (selection.rangeCount > 0) {
                        const range = selection.getRangeAt(0);
                        range.deleteContents();
                    }
                    showTemporaryMessage(`تم الوصول للحد الأقصى: ${MAX_CHARS_DEFAULT} حرف`, 2000);
                }
            });
        }

        // ============ REST OF THE FUNCTIONS (UNCHANGED) ============
        function initFileUpload() {
            const fileUploadArea = document.getElementById('file-upload-area');
            const fileInput = document.getElementById('file-input');

            if (!fileUploadArea || !fileInput) return;

            fileUploadArea.addEventListener('click', () => {
                fileInput.click();
            });

            fileUploadArea.addEventListener('dragover', (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                fileUploadArea.style.borderColor = '#2563eb';
                fileUploadArea.style.background = '#eff6ff';
            });

            fileUploadArea.addEventListener('dragleave', (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                fileUploadArea.style.borderColor = '#d1d5db';
                fileUploadArea.style.background = '#f9fafb';
            });

            fileUploadArea.addEventListener('drop', (e) => {
                e.preventDefault();
                fileUploadArea.style.borderColor = '#d1d5db';
                fileUploadArea.style.background = '#f9fafb';
                
                const files = e.dataTransfer.files;
                if (files.length > 0) {
                    handleFileUpload(files[0]);
                }
            });

            fileInput.addEventListener('change', (e) => {
                if (e.target.files.length > 0) {
                    handleFileUpload(e.target.files[0]);
                }
            });
        }
async function extractTextFromPDF(arrayBuffer) {
    try {
        const pdf = await pdfjsLib.getDocument(arrayBuffer).promise;
        let fullText = '';
        
        for (let i = 1; i <= pdf.numPages; i++) {
            const page = await pdf.getPage(i);
            const textContent = await page.getTextContent();
            const pageText = textContent.items.map(item => item.str).join(' ');
            fullText += pageText + '\n';
        }
        
        return fullText;
    } catch (error) {
        console.error('PDF extraction error:', error);
        throw new Error('تعذر قراءة ملف PDF');
    }
}
async function getTextContentFromFile(file, content) {
    const fileExtension = file.name.split('.').pop().toLowerCase();
    let extractedText = '';
    
    switch (fileExtension) {
        case 'txt':
            extractedText = content;
            break;
            
        case 'pdf':
            extractedText = await extractTextFromPDF(content);
            break;
            
        case 'docx':
            extractedText = await extractTextFromDOCX(content);
            break;
            
        case 'xlsx':
            showError('ملفات Excel غير مدعومة حالياً. يرجى تحويل البيانات إلى ملف نصي.');
            return '';
            
        default:
            showError('نوع الملف غير مدعوم');
            return '';
    }
    
    return cleanAndFilterText(extractedText);
}

// دالة استخراج النص من DOCX
async function extractTextFromDOCX(arrayBuffer) {
    try {
        const result = await mammoth.extractRawText({arrayBuffer: arrayBuffer});
        return result.value;
    } catch (error) {
        console.error('DOCX extraction error:', error);
        throw new Error('تعذر قراءة ملف Word');
    }
}

async function handleFileUpload(file) {
    const maxSize = 50 * 1024 * 1024; // 50MB
    
    const allowedTypes = ['txt', 'pdf', 'docx', 'xlsx'];
    const fileExtension = file.name.split('.').pop().toLowerCase();
    
    if (!allowedTypes.includes(fileExtension)) {
        showError('نوع الملف غير مدعوم. الملفات المدعومة: .txt, .pdf, .docx, .xlsx');
        return;
    }
    
    if (file.size > maxSize) {
        showError('حجم الملف كبير جداً. الحد الأقصى 50MB');
        return;
    }

    // عرض رسالة تحميل
    showTemporaryMessage('جاري معالجة الملف...', 3000);
    
    try {
        let content;
        
        if (fileExtension === 'txt') {
            content = await readFileAsText(file);
        } else {
            content = await readFileAsArrayBuffer(file);
        }
        
        const extractedText = await getTextContentFromFile(file, content);
        if (!extractedText) return;
        
        const trimmedContent = extractedText.substring(0, MAX_CHARS_DEFAULT);
        
        // Switch to input text tab and populate content
        document.querySelector('[data-tab="guided_selection"]').click();
        document.getElementById('simple-text-input').value = trimmedContent;
setTimeout(() => {
    updateCurrentEditorDirection();
}, 100);

        updateCharCount();
        saveTextToStorage();
        
        showSuccess(`تم تحميل الملف بنجاح. تم استخراج ${trimmedContent.length} حرف من أصل ${extractedText.length}.`);
        
    } catch (error) {
        console.error('File processing error:', error);
        showError('خطأ في معالجة الملف: ' + error.message);
    }
}

// دوال مساعدة لقراءة الملفات
function readFileAsText(file) {
    return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
        const reader = new FileReader();
        reader.onload = (e) => resolve(e.target.result);
        reader.onerror = () => reject(new Error('خطأ في قراءة الملف'));
        reader.readAsText(file, 'UTF-8');
    });
}

function readFileAsArrayBuffer(file) {
    return new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
        const reader = new FileReader();
        reader.onload = (e) => resolve(e.target.result);
        reader.onerror = () => reject(new Error('خطأ في قراءة الملف'));
        reader.readAsArrayBuffer(file);
    });
}


 

// دالة تنظيف وفلترة النص - أضف هذه الدالة الجديدة
function cleanAndFilterText(text) {
    if (!text) return '';
    
    // إزالة الرموز غير المرغوب فيها
    let cleanText = text
        .replace(/[\x00-\x08\x0B\x0C\x0E-\x1F\x7F-\x84\x86-\x9F]/g, '') // إزالة رموز التحكم
        .replace(/[^\u0000-\u007F\u0600-\u06FF\u0750-\u077F\u08A0-\u08FF\s\p{P}\p{N}]/gu, '') // الاحتفاظ بالعربية والإنجليزية والأرقام والترقيم فقط
        .replace(/\s+/g, ' ') // توحيد المسافات
        .replace(/[\r\n]+/g, '\n') // توحيد أسطر الفواصل
        .trim(); // إزالة المسافات من البداية والنهاية
    
    // فلترة الجمل الفارغة
    cleanText = cleanText
        .split('\n')
        .filter(line => line.trim().length > 0)
        .join('\n');
    
    // إزالة التكرارات المفرطة
    cleanText = cleanText.replace(/(.)\1{4,}/g, '$1$1$1'); // تقليل التكرار لأكثر من 3 مرات
    
    return cleanText;
}


        function extractStringsFromJson(obj) {
            let text = '';
            if (typeof obj === 'string') {
                text += obj + ' ';
            } else if (Array.isArray(obj)) {
                for (const item of obj) {
                    text += extractStringsFromJson(item);
                }
            } else if (typeof obj === 'object' && obj !== null) {
                for (const key in obj) {
                    if (Object.hasOwnProperty.call(obj, key)) {
                        text += extractStringsFromJson(obj[key]);
                    }
                }
            }
            return text;
        }

        // ============ EMOTION SYSTEM ============
function initEmotionSystem() {
    const emotionTrigger = document.getElementById('emotion-selector-trigger');
    const emotionDropdown = document.getElementById('emotion-selector-dropdown');
    const clearEmotionsBtn = document.getElementById('clear-emotions-btn');
    const smartTextEditor = document.getElementById('smart-text-editor');

    if (!emotionTrigger || !emotionDropdown || !smartTextEditor) return;
    
    // تجنب التهيئة المتكررة
    if (emotionSystemInitialized) {
        console.log('Emotion system already initialized, skipping...');
        return;
    }

    console.log('Initializing emotion system with autocomplete...');

    // إنشاء dropdown الخاص بالـ autocomplete إذا لم يكن موجوداً
    let autocompleteDropdown = document.getElementById('emotion-autocomplete-dropdown');
    if (!autocompleteDropdown) {
        autocompleteDropdown = createAutocompleteDropdown();
    }

    // إزالة أي event listeners قديمة
    const newEmotionTrigger = emotionTrigger.cloneNode(true);
    emotionTrigger.parentNode.replaceChild(newEmotionTrigger, emotionTrigger);
    
    const newClearBtn = clearEmotionsBtn.cloneNode(true);
    clearEmotionsBtn.parentNode.replaceChild(newClearBtn, clearEmotionsBtn);

    // إعادة تعريف المراجع
    const emotionTriggerNew = document.getElementById('emotion-selector-trigger');
    const clearEmotionsBtnNew = document.getElementById('clear-emotions-btn');

    // ===== إدارة Focus Position =====
    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('blur', saveFocusPosition);
    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('keyup', saveFocusPosition);
    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('mouseup', saveFocusPosition);
    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('focus', restoreFocusPosition);

    // ===== إدارة Emotion Dropdown التقليدي =====
    emotionTriggerNew.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        e.stopPropagation();
        hideAutocomplete(); // إخفاء autocomplete عند فتح dropdown التقليدي
        const isVisible = emotionDropdown.style.display !== 'none';
        emotionDropdown.style.display = isVisible ? 'none' : 'block';
        emotionTriggerNew.classList.toggle('active', !isVisible);
    });

    // إغلاق dropdown عند النقر خارجه
    document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        if (!emotionDropdown.contains(e.target) && !emotionTriggerNew.contains(e.target)) {
            emotionDropdown.style.display = 'none';
            emotionTriggerNew.classList.remove('active');
        }
    });

    // إضافة emotion من dropdown التقليدي
    emotionDropdown.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        const option = e.target.closest('.emotion-option');
        if (option) {
            e.preventDefault();
            e.stopPropagation();
            
            const tag = option.getAttribute('data-tag');
            const category = option.getAttribute('data-category');
            
            insertEmotionTag(tag, category);
            emotionDropdown.style.display = 'none';
            emotionTriggerNew.classList.remove('active');
        }
    });

    // ===== نظام Autocomplete الجديد =====
    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
        handleAutocompleteInput(e);
        updateCharCount();
        saveTextToStorage();
        
        // تحديث اتجاه النص تلقائياً
        setTimeout(() => {
            const plainText = getPlainTextFromEditor();
            const direction = detectTextDirection(plainText);
            applyTextDirection(smartTextEditor, direction);
        }, 50);
    });

    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('keydown', (e) => {
        // تعامل مع autocomplete أولاً
        if (handleAutocompleteKeydown(e)) {
            return;
        }
        
        // باقي معالجة الأحداث
        if (e.key === 'Enter') {
            e.preventDefault();
            document.execCommand('insertHTML', false, '<br><br>');
            return;
        }
        
        if (e.key === 'Backspace' || e.key === 'Delete') {
            const selection = window.getSelection();
            if (selection.rangeCount > 0) {
                const range = selection.getRangeAt(0);
                const container = range.commonAncestorContainer;
                const emotionTag = container.closest?.('.emotion-tag') || 
                                 (container.parentElement?.closest('.emotion-tag'));
                
                if (emotionTag) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    removeEmotionTag(emotionTag);
                    return;
                }
            }
        }
    });

    // معالجة اللصق
    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('paste', (e) => {
        e.preventDefault();
        hideAutocomplete(); // إخفاء autocomplete عند اللصق
        const text = (e.clipboardData || window.clipboardData).getData('text/plain');
        document.execCommand('insertHTML', false, escapeHtml(text));
        setTimeout(() => {
            updateCharCount();
            saveTextToStorage();
            updateCurrentEditorDirection();
        }, 100);
    });

    // ===== إدارة النقر على emotion tags =====
    smartTextEditor.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
        const emotionTag = e.target.closest('.emotion-tag');
        if (emotionTag) {
            e.preventDefault();
            hideAutocomplete(); // إخفاء autocomplete عند النقر على tag
            handleEmotionTagClick(emotionTag);
        }
    });

    // إضافة clear emotions
    if (clearEmotionsBtnNew) {
        clearEmotionsBtnNew.addEventListener('click', () => {
            hideAutocomplete();
            clearAllEmotions();
        });
    }

    emotionSystemInitialized = true;
    console.log('Emotion system with autocomplete initialized successfully');
}


function handleAutocompleteInput(e) {
    const smartTextEditor = document.getElementById('smart-text-editor');
    if (!smartTextEditor) return;
    
    const selection = window.getSelection();
    if (selection.rangeCount === 0) return;
    
    const range = selection.getRangeAt(0);
    const textNode = range.startContainer;
    
    if (textNode.nodeType !== Node.TEXT_NODE) {
        hideAutocomplete();
        return;
    }
    
    const textContent = textNode.textContent;
    const cursorPosition = range.startOffset;
    
    // البحث عن آخر "/" قبل المؤشر
    const textBeforeCursor = textContent.substring(0, cursorPosition);
    const lastSlashIndex = textBeforeCursor.lastIndexOf('/');
    
    if (lastSlashIndex === -1) {
        hideAutocomplete();
        return;
    }
    
    // استخراج النص بعد "/"
    const searchText = textBeforeCursor.substring(lastSlashIndex + 1);
    
    // التحقق من أن النص ليس فيه مسافات
    if (searchText.includes(' ') || searchText.includes('\n')) {
        hideAutocomplete();
        return;
    }
    
    console.log('Autocomplete search text:', searchText);
    
    if (searchText.length === 0) {
        showAutocompleteResults('', lastSlashIndex, textNode, range);
    } else if (searchText.length >= 1) {
        showAutocompleteResults(searchText, lastSlashIndex, textNode, range);
    }
}

function showAutocompleteResults(searchText, slashIndex, textNode, range) {
    let autocompleteDropdown = document.getElementById('emotion-autocomplete-dropdown');
    if (!autocompleteDropdown) {
        autocompleteDropdown = createAutocompleteDropdown();
    }
    
    // البحث في قائمة المشاعر
    const matches = findEmotionMatches(searchText);
    
    console.log('Found matches:', matches.length);
    
    if (matches.length === 0) {
        hideAutocomplete();
        return;
    }
    
    // حفظ معلومات الموضع
    autocompleteRange = range.cloneRange();
    autocompleteRange.setStart(textNode, slashIndex);
    autocompleteRange.setEnd(textNode, slashIndex + searchText.length + 1);
    currentAutocompleteText = '/' + searchText;
    
    // حساب موضع الـ dropdown
    const rect = range.getBoundingClientRect();
    
    autocompleteDropdown.style.top = (rect.bottom + window.scrollY + 5) + 'px';
    autocompleteDropdown.style.left = (rect.left + window.scrollX) + 'px';
    
    // ملء الـ dropdown بالنتائج
    autocompleteDropdown.innerHTML = '';
    
    matches.slice(0, 8).forEach(emotionTag => {
        const item = createAutocompleteItem(emotionTag, searchText);
        if (item) {
            autocompleteDropdown.appendChild(item);
        }
    });
    
    autocompleteDropdown.style.display = 'block';
    emotionAutocompleteActive = true;
    
    console.log('Autocomplete dropdown shown with', matches.length, 'results');
}

function findEmotionMatches(searchText) {
    const searchLower = searchText.toLowerCase().trim();
    const matches = [];
    
    console.log('Searching for:', searchLower);
    
    // إذا كان البحث فارغ، اعرض أهم المشاعر
    if (searchLower === '') {
        return ['[laughs]', '[sighs]', '[whisper tone]', '[happy tone]', '[sad tone]', '[angry tone]', '[excited tone]', '[dramatic tone]'];
    }
    
    // البحث المباشر في EMOTION_SEARCH_MAP
    for (const [key, tag] of Object.entries(EMOTION_SEARCH_MAP)) {
        if (key.toLowerCase().includes(searchLower)) {
            if (!matches.includes(tag)) {
                matches.push(tag);
                console.log('Found match via search map:', key, '->', tag);
            }
        }
    }
    
    // البحث في أسماء المشاعر
    for (const [tag, info] of Object.entries(ALL_EMOTION_TAGS)) {
        if (info.name.includes(searchLower)) {
            if (!matches.includes(tag)) {
                matches.push(tag);
                console.log('Found match via name:', info.name, '->', tag);
            }
        }
    }
    
    console.log('Total matches found:', matches.length);
    return matches;
}

function selectAutocompleteEmotion(emotionTag) {
    console.log('Selecting autocomplete emotion:', emotionTag);
    
    const smartTextEditor = document.getElementById('smart-text-editor');
    if (!smartTextEditor || !autocompleteRange) {
        console.error('Missing editor or range for autocomplete selection');
        hideAutocomplete();
        return;
    }
    
    // حذف النص المكتوب (/ + النص)
    const selection = window.getSelection();
    selection.removeAllRanges();
    selection.addRange(autocompleteRange);
    
    // حذف المحتوى المحدد
    autocompleteRange.deleteContents();
    
    // إنشاء emotion tag
    const emotionInfo = ALL_EMOTION_TAGS[emotionTag];
    const emotionSpan = document.createElement('span');
    emotionSpan.className = `emotion-tag ${emotionInfo.color}`;
    emotionSpan.contentEditable = false;
    emotionSpan.dataset.tag = emotionTag;
    emotionSpan.title = `${emotionInfo.name} - انقر للحذف`;
    emotionSpan.innerHTML = `<i class="fa-solid ${emotionInfo.icon}"></i> ${emotionInfo.name}`;
    
    // إدراج الـ tag
    autocompleteRange.insertNode(emotionSpan);
    
    // إضافة مسافة بعد الـ tag
    const spaceAfter = document.createTextNode(' ');
    autocompleteRange.setStartAfter(emotionSpan);
    autocompleteRange.insertNode(spaceAfter);
    
    // وضع المؤشر بعد المسافة
    autocompleteRange.setStartAfter(spaceAfter);
    autocompleteRange.collapse(true);
    selection.removeAllRanges();
    selection.addRange(autocompleteRange);
    
    // حفظ الموضع الجديد
    saveFocusPosition();
    
    hideAutocomplete();
    updateCharCount();
    saveTextToStorage();
    
    // تحديث اتجاه النص
    setTimeout(() => {
        updateCurrentEditorDirection();
    }, 100);
    
    // الاحتفاظ بالتركيز
    smartTextEditor.focus();
    
    showTemporaryMessage(`تم إضافة: ${emotionInfo.name}`, 1000);
}

function handleAutocompleteKeydown(e) {
    if (!emotionAutocompleteActive) return false;
    
    const autocompleteDropdown = document.getElementById('emotion-autocomplete-dropdown');
    if (!autocompleteDropdown || autocompleteDropdown.style.display === 'none') {
        return false;
    }
    
    const items = autocompleteDropdown.querySelectorAll('.autocomplete-item');
    let selectedIndex = Array.from(items).findIndex(item => 
        item.classList.contains('selected'));
    
    switch (e.key) {
        case 'ArrowDown':
            e.preventDefault();
            selectedIndex = selectedIndex < 0 ? 0 : Math.min(selectedIndex + 1, items.length - 1);
            updateAutocompleteSelection(items, selectedIndex);
            return true;
            
        case 'ArrowUp':
            e.preventDefault();
            selectedIndex = selectedIndex < 0 ? 0 : Math.max(selectedIndex - 1, 0);
            updateAutocompleteSelection(items, selectedIndex);
            return true;
            
        case 'Enter':
        case 'Tab':
            e.preventDefault();
            if (selectedIndex >= 0 && items[selectedIndex]) {
                const emotionTag = items[selectedIndex].dataset.emotionTag;
                if (emotionTag) {
                    selectAutocompleteEmotion(emotionTag);
                }
            } else if (items.length > 0) {
                const emotionTag = items[0].dataset.emotionTag;
                if (emotionTag) {
                    selectAutocompleteEmotion(emotionTag);
                }
            }
            return true;
            
        case 'Escape':
            e.preventDefault();
            hideAutocomplete();
            return true;
            
        case ' ':
            hideAutocomplete();
            return false;
            
        default:
            return false;
    }
}

function hideAutocomplete() {
    const autocompleteDropdown = document.getElementById('emotion-autocomplete-dropdown');
    if (autocompleteDropdown) {
        autocompleteDropdown.style.display = 'none';
        autocompleteDropdown.innerHTML = '';
    }
    
    emotionAutocompleteActive = false;
    autocompleteRange = null;
    currentAutocompleteText = '';
    
    console.log('Autocomplete hidden');
}
 
function showDirectionIndicator(direction) {
    // إزالة أي مؤشر سابق
    const existingIndicator = document.getElementById('direction-indicator');
    if (existingIndicator) {
        existingIndicator.remove();
    }
    
    const indicator = document.createElement('div');
    indicator.id = 'direction-indicator';
    indicator.style.cssText = `
        position: fixed;
        top: 20px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        background: #10b981;
        color: white;
        padding: 4px 12px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 500;
        z-index: 1000;
        opacity: 0.8;
        pointer-events: none;
        transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
    `;
    
    const directionText = {
        'rtl': '🔄 عربي (من اليمين لليسار)',
        'ltr': '🔄 English (Left to Right)', 
        'auto': '🔄 تلقائي'
    };
    
    indicator.textContent = directionText[direction] || directionText['auto'];
    document.body.appendChild(indicator);
    
    // إخفاء المؤشر بعد ثانيتين
    setTimeout(() => {
        if (indicator.parentNode) {
            indicator.style.opacity = '0';
            setTimeout(() => {
                if (indicator.parentNode) {
                    indicator.parentNode.removeChild(indicator);
                }
            }, 300);
        }
    }, 2000);
}

 
function updateAutocompleteSelection(items, selectedIndex) {
    items.forEach((item, index) => {
        if (index === selectedIndex) {
            item.classList.add('selected');
            item.style.backgroundColor = document.body.classList.contains('dark') ? '#475569' : '#e5e7eb';
            item.scrollIntoView({ block: 'nearest' });
        } else {
            item.classList.remove('selected');
            item.style.backgroundColor = 'transparent';
        }
    });
}

 

// إخفاء autocomplete عند النقر خارجه
document.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
    const autocompleteDropdown = document.getElementById('emotion-autocomplete-dropdown');
    const smartTextEditor = document.getElementById('smart-text-editor');
    
    if (autocompleteDropdown && 
        !autocompleteDropdown.contains(e.target) && 
        !smartTextEditor?.contains(e.target)) {
        hideAutocomplete();
    }
});

function setupEmotionSystem() {
    // هذه الدالة لم تعد مطلوبة لأن كل شيء تم نقله إلى initEmotionSystem
    // يمكنك حذفها بالكامل أو تركها فارغة
    return;
}

function initSmartTextEditor() {
    if (currentInputMode !== 'emotion_text') return;

    console.log('Initializing smart text editor...');

    // Initialize emotion system only once
    initEmotionSystem();
    updateTextDirection();

    // Load stored content
    const storedText = localStorage.getItem('lahajati_tts_superior_emotion_text');
    if (storedText) {
        const smartTextEditor = document.getElementById('smart-text-editor');
        if (smartTextEditor) {
            smartTextEditor.innerHTML = processTextWithEmotions(storedText);
            updateCharCount();
            updateTextDirection();
        }
    }

    console.log('Smart text editor initialized');
}

function insertEmotionTag(tag, category) {
    const smartTextEditor = document.getElementById('smart-text-editor');
    if (!smartTextEditor) return;
    
    // Ensure editor is focused
    smartTextEditor.focus();
    
    const emotionInfo = ALL_EMOTION_TAGS[tag] || { 
        name: tag, 
        icon: 'fa-face-smile', 
        color: 'emotion' 
    };
    
    const emotionSpan = document.createElement('span');
    emotionSpan.className = `emotion-tag ${emotionInfo.color}`;
    emotionSpan.contentEditable = false;
    emotionSpan.dataset.tag = tag;
    emotionSpan.dataset.category = category;
    emotionSpan.title = `${emotionInfo.name} - انقر للحذف`;
    emotionSpan.innerHTML = `<i class="fa-solid ${emotionInfo.icon}"></i> ${emotionInfo.name}`;
    
    // Try to restore the saved position first
    if (savedRange) {
        try {
            const selection = window.getSelection();
            selection.removeAllRanges();
            selection.addRange(savedRange);
        } catch (e) {
            placeCursorAtEnd();
        }
    }

    // Get current selection or cursor position
    const selection = window.getSelection();
    let range;
    
    if (selection.rangeCount > 0) {
        range = selection.getRangeAt(0);
    } else {
        // Create new range at the end if no selection
        range = document.createRange();
        range.selectNodeContents(smartTextEditor);
        range.collapse(false);
    }

    // Clear any existing selection content
    range.deleteContents();
    
    // Add space before if needed (check if previous character is not a space or newline)
    const startContainer = range.startContainer;
    let needsSpaceBefore = false;
