<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/flowbite/2.3.0/flowbite.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sweetalert2@11"></script>
<script src="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.4/dist/aos.js"></script>

<script>
document.addEventListener('alpine:init', () => {
    Alpine.store('app', {
        isCouponModalOpen: false,
        couponCode: '',
        activateCoupon() {
            if (!this.couponCode.trim()) {
                Swal.fire({
                    icon: 'error',
                    title: 'Error',
                    text: 'app.coupon_required',
                    confirmButtonColor: '#9333ea'
                });
                return;
            }
            console.log('Attempting to activate coupon:', this.couponCode);
            Swal.fire({
                icon: 'success',
                title: 'Success!',
                text: 'app.coupon_applied_placeholder',
                showConfirmButton: false,
                timer: 2000
            });
            this.isCouponModalOpen = false;
            this.couponCode = '';
        }
    });

    // AI Chat Widget Component
    Alpine.data('aiChatWidget', () => ({
        isOpen: false,
        isTyping: false,
        currentMessage: '',
        messages: [],
        currentSessionId: null,
        audioElements: new Map(),
        activeTab: 'chat',
chatSessions: [{"session_id":"chat_6912c20c7b34d_1762837004","title":"How can I find voice id","messages_count":4,"updated_at_human":"8 hours ago"}],

        
        // Settings
        selectedVoiceId: '1408',
        selectedDialectId: '',
        assistantPersonality: 'professional',
        preferredSpeed: 1,
        
        init() {
            // Load saved session from localStorage
            const savedSessionId = localStorage.getItem('aiChatSessionId');
            if (savedSessionId) {
                this.currentSessionId = savedSessionId;
                this.loadChatHistory();
            }
            
            console.log('AI Chat Widget initialized');
        },
        
        toggleChat() {
            this.isOpen = !this.isOpen;
            if (this.isOpen) {
                this.$nextTick(() => {
                    this.scrollToBottom();
                });
            }
        },
        
        closeChat() {
            this.isOpen = false;
        },
        
        switchTab(tab) {
            this.activeTab = tab;
            if (tab === 'history') {
                this.loadChatSessions();
            }
        },
        
        startNewChat() {
            this.currentSessionId = null;
            this.messages = [];
            localStorage.removeItem('aiChatSessionId');
            this.activeTab = 'chat';
            
            // Remove active class from all sessions
            this.chatSessions.forEach(session => {
                session.active = false;
            });
            
            this.showToast('success', 'محادثة جديدة', 'تم بدء محادثة جديدة');
        },
        
        async sendMessage() {
            const message = this.currentMessage.trim();
            if (!message || this.isTyping) return;
            
            // Add user message
            this.addMessage('user', message);
            this.currentMessage = '';
            
            // Show typing indicator
            this.isTyping = true;
            this.scrollToBottom();
            
            try {
                const response = await fetch('https://lahajati.ai/en/ai-chat/process', {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: {
                        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                        'X-CSRF-TOKEN': document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').content
                    },
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        message: message,
                        session_id: this.currentSessionId,
                        voice_id: this.selectedVoiceId,
                        dialect_id: this.selectedDialectId
                    })
                });
                
                const data = await response.json();
                
                if (data.success) {
                    this.currentSessionId = data.session_id;
                    localStorage.setItem('aiChatSessionId', data.session_id);
                    
                    // Add bot response
                    this.addMessage('bot', data.message, data.audio_data, data.message_id);
                    
                    // Update chat sessions list
                    this.updateChatSessionsList(data.session_id, message);
                    
                    // Update balance if needed
                    if (document.getElementById("userBalanceNavBar") && 3 <= 4) {
                        const currentBalance = parseInt(document.getElementById("userBalanceNavBar").textContent.replace(/\D/g,'')) || 0;
                        const userBalanceNavBar = document.getElementById("userBalanceNavBar");
                        if(userBalanceNavBar) userBalanceNavBar.textContent = Math.max(0, currentBalance - (data.cost || 0));
                    }
                } else {
                    this.addMessage('bot', data.message || 'عذراً، حدث خطأ في معالجة طلبك.');
                    this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'حدث خطأ في معالجة الطلب');
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Chat error:', error);
                this.addMessage('bot', 'عذراً، حدث خطأ في الاتصال. يرجى المحاولة مرة أخرى.');
                this.showToast('error', 'خطأ في الاتصال', 'يرجى التحقق من اتصال الإنترنت');
            } finally {
                this.isTyping = false;
                this.scrollToBottom();
            }
        },
        
        sendQuickMessage(message) {
            this.currentMessage = message;
            this.sendMessage();
        },
        
      addMessage(type, content, audioData = null, messageId = null) {
    const now = new Date();
    const timeString = now.getHours().toString().padStart(2, '0') + ':' + 
                      now.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2, '0');

    const message = {
        id: Date.now() + Math.random(),
        type: type,
        content: content,
        time: timeString,
        audio: audioData,
        messageId: messageId,
        isPlaying: false,
        progress: 0,
        audioTime: '0:00 / 0:00'
    };
    
    this.messages.push(message);
    this.$nextTick(() => {
        this.scrollToBottom();
        // لا نحتاج استدعاء initAudioPlayer بعد الآن
    });
},
        
        formatMessage(content) {
            // Format message content
            content = content.replace(/(https?:\/\/[^\s]+)/g, '<a href="$1" target="_blank" class="text-blue-400 underline">$1</a>');
            content = content.replace(/\n/g, '<br>');
            content = content.replace(/\*\*(.*?)\*\*/g, '<strong>$1</strong>');
            content = content.replace(/\*(.*?)\*/g, '<em>$1</em>');
            return content;
        },
        
        scrollToBottom() {
            this.$nextTick(() => {
                const container = this.$refs.messagesContainer;
                if (container) {
                    container.scrollTop = container.scrollHeight;
                }
            });
        },
        
        autoResize(textarea) {
            textarea.style.height = 'auto';
            textarea.style.height = Math.min(textarea.scrollHeight, 120) + 'px';
        },
        
        // Audio Player Functions
initAudioPlayer(message) {
    this.$nextTick(() => {
        // البحث عن عنصر الصوت بطريقة أفضل
        const audioElements = this.$refs.messagesContainer.querySelectorAll('audio');
        let targetAudio = null;
        
        // البحث عن الصوت الصحيح
        audioElements.forEach(audio => {
            const source = audio.querySelector('source');
            if (source && source.src.includes(message.audio.substring(0, 30))) {
                targetAudio = audio;
            }
        });
        
        // إذا لم نجد الصوت، ابحث بطريقة أخرى
        if (!targetAudio) {
            const messageElements = this.$refs.messagesContainer.querySelectorAll('.ai-message');
            messageElements.forEach(messageEl => {
                const audio = messageEl.querySelector('audio');
                if (audio) {
                    const source = audio.querySelector('source');
                    if (source && source.src.includes('base64')) {
                        // تحقق من أن هذا هو الصوت الصحيح
                        const audioData = source.src.split('base64,')[1];
                        if (audioData && audioData.substring(0, 30) === message.audio.substring(0, 30)) {
                            targetAudio = audio;
                        }
                    }
                }
            });
        }
        
        if (targetAudio) {
            this.audioElements.set(message.id, targetAudio);
            
            // إضافة event listeners
            targetAudio.addEventListener('loadedmetadata', () => {
                this.updateAudioTime(message);
            });
            
            targetAudio.addEventListener('timeupdate', () => {
                this.updateAudioProgress(message);
                this.updateAudioTime(message);
            });
            
            targetAudio.addEventListener('ended', () => {
                this.onAudioEnded(message);
            });
            
            // تحميل الصوت
            targetAudio.load();
        }
    });
},

        
toggleAudio(messageId) {
    const message = this.messages.find(m => m.id === messageId);
    if (!message || !message.audio) {
        console.log('Message or audio not found');
        return;
    }
    
    // إيقاف جميع الأصوات الأخرى أولاً
    this.audioElements.forEach((audioEl, id) => {
        if (id !== messageId && !audioEl.paused) {
            audioEl.pause();
            const msg = this.messages.find(m => m.id === id);
            if (msg) msg.isPlaying = false;
        }
    });
    
    // البحث عن عنصر الصوت أو إنشاؤه
    let audio = this.audioElements.get(messageId);
    
    if (!audio) {
        // إنشاء عنصر صوت جديد
        audio = new Audio();
        
        // تحديد المصدر حسب النوع
        if (message.audio.startsWith('http')) {
            audio.src = message.audio;
        } else {
            audio.src = `data:audio/mpeg;base64,${message.audio}`;
        }
        
        // إضافة المستمعين
        audio.addEventListener('timeupdate', () => {
            this.updateAudioProgress(message);
            this.updateAudioTime(message);
        });
        
        audio.addEventListener('ended', () => {
            this.onAudioEnded(message);
        });
        
        audio.addEventListener('loadedmetadata', () => {
            this.updateAudioTime(message);
        });
        
        audio.addEventListener('error', (e) => {
            console.error('Audio error:', e);
            message.isPlaying = false;
            this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'لا يمكن تشغيل الملف الصوتي');
        });
        
        // حفظ المرجع
        this.audioElements.set(messageId, audio);
    }
    
    // تشغيل أو إيقاف
    if (audio.paused) {
        audio.play().then(() => {
            message.isPlaying = true;
            console.log('Audio playing');
        }).catch(error => {
            console.error('Play error:', error);
            message.isPlaying = false;
            this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'فشل في تشغيل الصوت');
        });
    } else {
        audio.pause();
        message.isPlaying = false;
    }
},

        
        seekAudio(message, event) {
            const audio = this.audioElements.get(message.id);
            if (!audio || isNaN(audio.duration)) return;
            
            const rect = event.currentTarget.getBoundingClientRect();
            const x = event.clientX - rect.left;
            const percentage = x / rect.width;
            audio.currentTime = audio.duration * percentage;
        },
        
        updateAudioProgress(message) {
            const audio = this.audioElements.get(message.id);
            if (audio && !isNaN(audio.duration)) {
                message.progress = (audio.currentTime / audio.duration) * 100;
            }
        },
        
        updateAudioTime(message) {
            const audio = this.audioElements.get(message.id);
            if (audio) {
                const formatTime = (seconds) => {
                    if (isNaN(seconds)) return '0:00';
                    const mins = Math.floor(seconds / 60);
                    const secs = Math.floor(seconds % 60);
                    return `${mins}:${secs.toString().padStart(2, '0')}`;
                };
                
                const current = formatTime(audio.currentTime);
                const duration = formatTime(audio.duration);
                message.audioTime = `${current} / ${duration}`;
            }
        },
        
        onAudioEnded(message) {
            message.isPlaying = false;
            message.progress = 0;
        },
        
        downloadAudio(message) {
            if (!message.audio) return;
            
            const link = document.createElement('a');
            link.href = `data:audio/mpeg;base64,${message.audio}`;
            link.download = `lahajati_voice_${message.messageId || Date.now()}.mp3`;
            link.click();
            
            this.showToast('success', 'تم التحميل', 'تم تحميل الملف الصوتي بنجاح');
        },
        
        shareAudio(message) {
            if (!message.audio) return;
            
            if (navigator.share) {
                const blob = this.base64ToBlob(message.audio, 'audio/mpeg');
                const file = new File([blob], 'lahajati_voice.mp3', { type: 'audio/mpeg' });
                
                navigator.share({
                    files: [file],
                    title: 'صوت من لهجاتي AI',
                    text: 'استمع لهذا الصوت المذهل!'
                }).then(() => {
                    this.showToast('success', 'تمت المشاركة', 'تم مشاركة الملف بنجاح');
                }).catch(err => {
                    console.log('Share cancelled or failed:', err);
                });
            } else {
                this.showToast('info', 'المشاركة', 'المشاركة غير مدعومة في هذا المتصفح');
            }
        },
        
        base64ToBlob(base64, contentType) {
            const byteCharacters = atob(base64);
            const byteArrays = [];
            
            for (let offset = 0; offset < byteCharacters.length; offset += 512) {
                const slice = byteCharacters.slice(offset, offset + 512);
                const byteNumbers = new Array(slice.length);
                
                for (let i = 0; i < slice.length; i++) {
                    byteNumbers[i] = slice.charCodeAt(i);
                }
                
                const byteArray = new Uint8Array(byteNumbers);
                byteArrays.push(byteArray);
            }
            
            return new Blob(byteArrays, { type: contentType });
        },
        
        // Settings Functions
        async saveSettings() {
            try {
                const response = await fetch('https://lahajati.ai/en/ai-chat/preferences', {
                    method: 'POST',
                    headers: {
                        'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                        'X-CSRF-TOKEN': document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').content
                    },
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        assistant_personality: this.assistantPersonality,
                        preferred_speed: this.preferredSpeed,
                        preferred_voice_id: this.selectedVoiceId,
                        preferred_dialect_id: this.selectedDialectId
                    })
                });
                
                const data = await response.json();
                
                if (data.success) {
                    this.showToast('success', 'تم الحفظ', 'تم حفظ الإعدادات بنجاح');
                } else {
                    this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'فشل في حفظ الإعدادات');
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Settings error:', error);
                this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'حدث خطأ في حفظ الإعدادات');
            }
        },
        
        // History Functions
        async loadChatSessions() {
            try {
                const response = await fetch('https://lahajati.ai/ai-chat/sessions');
                const data = await response.json();
                
                if (data.success) {
                    this.chatSessions = data.sessions.map(session => ({
                        session_id: session.session_id,
                        title: session.title,
                        messages_count: session.messages_count,
                        updated_at_human: session.updated_at_human,
                        active: session.session_id === this.currentSessionId
                    }));
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Error loading chat sessions:', error);
            }
        },
        
        async loadChatSession(sessionId) {
            if (!sessionId) return;
            
            try {
                const response = await fetch(`https://lahajati.ai/ai-chat/session/${sessionId}`);
                const data = await response.json();
                
                if (data.success && data.messages) {
                    this.currentSessionId = sessionId;
                    localStorage.setItem('aiChatSessionId', sessionId);
                        const now = new Date(msg.created_at);
    const timeString = now.getHours().toString().padStart(2, '0') + ':' + 
                      now.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2, '0');
                    this.messages = data.messages.map(msg => ({
                        id: msg.id,
                        type: msg.type,
                        content: msg.content,
                        time: timeString,
                        audio: msg.audio_data,
                        messageId: msg.id,
                        isPlaying: false,
                        progress: 0,
                        audioTime: '0:00 / 0:00'
                    }));
                    
                    // Update active session
                    this.chatSessions.forEach(session => {
                        session.active = session.session_id === sessionId;
                    });
                    
                    this.activeTab = 'chat';
                    
                    this.$nextTick(() => {
                        this.messages.forEach(message => {
                            if (message.audio) {
                                this.initAudioPlayer(message);
                            }
                        });
                        this.scrollToBottom();
                    });
                    
                    this.showToast('success', 'تم التحميل', 'تم تحميل المحادثة بنجاح');
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Error loading chat session:', error);
                this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'فشل في تحميل المحادثة');
            }
        },
        
        async deleteSession(sessionId) {
            if (!confirm('هل أنت متأكد من حذف هذه المحادثة؟ لا يمكن التراجع عن هذا الإجراء.')) {
                return;
            }
            
            try {
                const response = await fetch(`https://lahajati.ai/ai-chat/session/${sessionId}`, {
                    method: 'DELETE',
                    headers: {
                        'X-CSRF-TOKEN': document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').content
                    }
                });
                
                const data = await response.json();
                
                if (data.success) {
                    // Remove from sessions list
                    this.chatSessions = this.chatSessions.filter(session => session.session_id !== sessionId);
                    
                    // If current session, start new chat
                    if (this.currentSessionId === sessionId) {
                        this.startNewChat();
                    }
                    
                    this.showToast('success', 'تم الحذف', 'تم حذف المحادثة بنجاح');
                } else {
                    this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'فشل في حذف المحادثة');
                }
            } catch (error) {
                console.error('Error deleting session:', error);
                this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'حدث خطأ في حذف المحادثة');
            }
        },
        
        updateChatSessionsList(sessionId, firstMessage) {
            const existingSession = this.chatSessions.find(s => s.session_id === sessionId);
            
            if (existingSession) {
                existingSession.messages_count++;
                existingSession.updated_at_human = 'الآن';
                existingSession.active = true;
            } else {
                this.chatSessions.unshift({
                    session_id: sessionId,
                    title: firstMessage.substring(0, 50) + (firstMessage.length > 50 ? '...' : ''),
                    messages_count: 1,
                    updated_at_human: 'الآن',
                    active: true
                });
            }
            
            // Remove active from other sessions
            this.chatSessions.forEach(session => {
                if (session.session_id !== sessionId) {
                    session.active = false;
                }
            });
        },
        
       async loadChatHistory() {
    if (!this.currentSessionId) return;
    
    try {
        const response = await fetch(`https://lahajati.ai/ai-chat/session/${this.currentSessionId}`);
        const data = await response.json();
        
        if (data.success && data.messages) {
            this.messages = data.messages.map(msg => {
                // إنشاء التاريخ لكل رسالة بشكل منفصل
                const messageDate = new Date(msg.created_at);
                
                // التحقق من صحة التاريخ
                let timeString;
                if (isNaN(messageDate.getTime())) {
                    // إذا كان التاريخ غير صحيح، استخدم الوقت الحالي
                    const now = new Date();
                    timeString = now.getHours().toString().padStart(2, '0') + ':' + 
                                now.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2, '0');
                } else {
                    // استخدام تاريخ الرسالة
                    timeString = messageDate.getHours().toString().padStart(2, '0') + ':' + 
                                messageDate.getMinutes().toString().padStart(2, '0');
                }
                
                return {
                    id: msg.id,
                    type: msg.type,
                    content: msg.content,
                    time: timeString,
                    audio: msg.audio_data,
                    messageId: msg.id,
                    isPlaying: false,
                    progress: 0,
                    audioTime: '0:00 / 0:00'
                };
            });
            
            this.$nextTick(() => {
                this.scrollToBottom();
                // لا نحتاج initAudioPlayer بعد الآن لأن toggleAudio يتولى الأمر
            });
        }
    } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error loading chat history:', error);
        this.showToast('error', 'خطأ', 'فشل في تحميل تاريخ المحادثة');
    }
},
        
        showToast(type, title, message) {
            // Simple toast notification
            const toast = document.createElement('div');
            toast.className = `fixed top-4 right-4 p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg z-50 max-w-sm ${
                type === 'success' ? 'bg-green-500' : 
                type === 'error' ? 'bg-red-500' : 
                type === 'warning' ? 'bg-yellow-500' : 'bg-blue-500'
            } text-white`;
            
            toast.innerHTML = `
                <div class="flex items-center">
                    <i class="fas fa-${
                        type === 'success' ? 'check-circle' : 
                        type === 'error' ? 'exclamation-circle' : 
                        type === 'warning' ? 'exclamation-triangle' : 'info-circle'
                    } mr-2"></i>
                    <div>
                        <div class="font-bold">${title}</div>
                        <div class="text-sm">${message}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            `;
            
            document.body.appendChild(toast);
            
            setTimeout(() => {
                toast.remove();
            }, 3000);
        }
    }));
});

function mainLayoutData() {
    return {
        theme: localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'system',
        showAnnouncement: false,
        
        applyTheme() {
            if (this.theme === 'dark' || (this.theme === 'system' && window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches)) {
                document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
            } else {
                document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
            }
        },
        
        closeAnnouncement() {
            this.showAnnouncement = false;
            fetch('/mark-announcement-seen', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                    'X-CSRF-TOKEN': document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').getAttribute('content'),
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                },
                body: JSON.stringify({
                    announcement_key: 'announcement_seen_v1.03_2025'
                })
            }).catch(console.error);
        },
        
        init() {
            AOS.init({ duration: 800, once: true });
            this.applyTheme();

            this.$watch('theme', (value) => {
                localStorage.setItem('theme', value);
                this.applyTheme();
            });

            window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').addEventListener('change', () => {
                if (this.theme === 'system') {
                    this.applyTheme();
                }
            });

                        this.initLastLoginUpdater();
            
            console.log('Alpine main layout initialized');
        },

                lastCallTime: 0,
        cooldown: 60000,
        updateLastLogin() {
            const currentTime = Date.now();
            if (currentTime - this.lastCallTime < this.cooldown) {
                return;
            }
            this.lastCallTime = currentTime;
            
            fetch('/update-last-login', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                    'X-CSRF-TOKEN': document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').getAttribute('content'),
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                    'Accept': 'application/json'
                },
                body: JSON.stringify({})
            })
            .then(response => {
                if (!response.ok) {
                    // console.error('Failed to update last login:', response.statusText);
                }
            })
            .catch(error => console.error('Error updating last login:', error));
        },
        
        initLastLoginUpdater() {
            const activityHandler = () => this.updateLastLogin();
            ['mousemove', 'keydown', 'scroll', 'touchstart', 'click'].forEach(evt => 
                document.addEventListener(evt, activityHandler, { passive: true })
            );
        },
        
        markNotificationAsRead(alertId, elementId) {
            fetch(`/tools/alerts/${alertId}/mark-as-read`, {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                    'X-CSRF-TOKEN': document.querySelector('meta[name="csrf-token"]').getAttribute('content'),
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json',
                    'Accept': 'application/json',
                },
            })
            .then(response => response.json())
            .then(data => {
                if (data.success) {
                    const badge = document.getElementById(elementId);
                    if (badge) {
                        badge.remove();
                    }
                }
            })
            .catch(error => console.error('Error marking notification as read:', error));
        }
            }
}
</script>
